the Council's one-day visit: a meeting with U.S. Secretary of
State Madeleine Albright; a meeting and lunch on Capitol Hill with
members of the Senate Foreign Relations and Armed Services
Committee; a call at the White House to meet deputy National
Security Adviser Jim Steinberg; and a dinner with Albright.
</P>
<P>
