<HEADLINE> U.S. Concerned About Arms Race in South Asia:  Congressman </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"We don't want the same kind of mistake to be repeated in the
region similar to the one during the Cold War era which had left
erstwhile U.S.S.R.(Soviet Union) bankrupt," Ackerman, heading a
