<TEXT>
<P>
MACAO, March 23 (Xinhua) -- The Macao meteorological station is
able to conduct weather analysis in an area as small as 18 by 18
km, meteorological experts here said Thursday.
</P>
<P>
The achievement was made with the help of a new set of device
which was put into formal operation on this World Meteorological
Day.
</P>
<P>
The news was released at a celebrating meeting with the
participation of officials and meteorological experts of the Macao
Special Administrative Region (SAR) of China.
</P>
