<HEADLINE> China Expects A Profitable Power Sector </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
To achieve the goal, the power conglomerate by restructuring
the power industry and developing more power grids, said Jiang
Shaojun, director of Strategic Studies and Planning Department
under CSPC.
</P>
<P>
China plans to establish a modern corporate system in the whole
power sector this year.
</P>
<P>
