club in Shanghai has become home of the Shanghai Art Gallery after
renovation.
</P>
<P>
The British style structure was completed in 1934. After new
China was founded in 1949, the building was first turned into a
museum and then a library.
</P>
<P>
The neo-classic style of the structure now remains the same,
except undergoing washing and repairing. Its interior has been
remodeled as demanded by an art gallery.
</P>
<P>
The new gallery, covering an area of 18,476 square meters,
boasts 12 exhibition halls along with conference rooms and snack
bars.  
