<HEADLINE> Brazil Asks EU to Cut Tariff on Agricultural Products </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BRASILIA, March 22 (Xinhua) -- A cut in tariffs by the European
Union (EU) on agricultural imports from Brazil would favor an
expansion of bilateral trade, Brazil's Agriculture Minister
Pratini de Moraes said Wednesday.
</P>
