pollution prevention, it is important to prioritize the
development of these facilities.
</P>
<P>
Manufacturers that produce these facilities and use Chinese
equipment may withhold corporate income equal to their investment,
according to the circular.
</P>
<P>
Taxes may also be waived for these enterprises that net less
than 3000,000 yuan (about 36,000 U.S. dollars) a year. The state
may also help pay for renovation or research by State-owned
enterprises engaged in environmental facility manufacture.
